and
just
as
she
rose
to
go
away,
she
said:
"Mademoiselle,
I
shall
not
soon
cease
to
regret
your
departure
from
my
establishment,
though
indeed
it
is
true
that
you
have
taught
your
class
of
pupils
so
well
that
they
are
all
quite
accomplished
in
the
little
works
you
manage
so
