whispered
"Hope
smiles
on
Effort!"
A
COMPETENCY
was
what
I
wanted;
a
competency
it
was
now
my
aim
and
resolve
to
secure;
but
never
had
I
been
farther
from
the
mark.
With
August
the
school
year
(l'annee
scolaire)
closed,
the
examinations
concluded,
the
prizes
were
adjudged,
the
schools
dispersed,
the
gates
of
all
colleges,
the
doors
of
all
