"because
you
fear
an
evil
which
may
never
happen!"
"It
will
happen;
you
KNOW
it
will,"
answered
that
stubborn
monitor,
Conscience.
"Do
what
you
feel
is
right;
obey
me,
and
even
in
the
sloughs
of
want
I
will
plant
for
you
