I
will
not
insult
you,
mademoiselle,
by
supposing
that
you
alluded
to
such
humbug."
"But
I
did
partly."
Hunsden
laughed
his
laugh
of
unmitigated
scorn.
"I
did,
Mr.
Hunsden.
Are
you
of
the
number
of
those
to
