and
to
leave
quite
out
of
my
heart
the
social
greatness
of
my
countrymen,
and
our
blood
earned
freedom,
and
the
natural
glories
of
our
mountains?
You're
mistaken
you're
mistaken."
"Social
greatness?
Call
it
what
you
will,
your
countrymen
are
sensible
