excitable
little
Helvetian
(by
the
by
she
has
infinitely
more
of
the
nervous,
mobile
Parisienne
in
her
than
of
the
the
robust
'jungfrau').
Your
Mdlle.
Henri
is
in
person
"chetive",
in
mind
"sans
caractere",
compared
with
the
queen
of
my
visions.
You,
