tractability
and
firmness:
I
sat
thinking
about
her,
and
wondering
what
her
plan
could
be,
when
she
re
entered.
"Monsieur,
I
have
given
Minnie"
(our
bonne)
"leave
to
go
out
too,
as
it
is
so
very
fine;
so
will
you
be
kind
enough
to
lock
the
door,
and
take
