were
like
inspiration;
in
one
there
was
such
a
flash,
in
the
other
such
a
power.
Half
an
hour
afterwards,
when
she
had
become
calm,
I
asked
where
all
that
wild
vigour
was
gone
which
had
transformed
her
ere
while
and
made
her
glance
so
